Package javax.slee.nullactivity

Interface Summary
NullActivity This interface is implemented by null activity objects.
NullActivityContextInterfaceFactory The Null Activity Context Interface Factory is used by SBBs to obtain an ActivityContextInterface object for a null activity.
NullActivityFactory The Null Activity Factory is used by SBBs to create new null activities.
